query: SELECT id, name, atoll, slug, CASE WHEN overview IS NOT NULL AND overview != '' THEN 'has content' ELSE 'empty' END as status FROM island_guides WHERE contentType = 'island' AND (name, atoll) IN (SELECT name, atoll FROM island_guides WHERE contentType = 'island' GROUP BY name, atoll HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) ORDER BY name, atoll, id
